1
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:08,070
[All of Her]

2
00:00:08,090 --> 00:00:10,250
[Episode 18]

3
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:15,680
Sometimes, I would imagine

4
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:17,080
to build a house in a place like this

5
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:19,800
and spend the rest of my life
with my beloved.

6
00:00:20,360 --> 00:00:21,840
But it's just wishful thinking.

7
00:00:23,040 --> 00:00:23,840
Life

8
00:00:24,320 --> 00:00:25,560
doesn't always go the way we want.

9
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:28,080
The more material wealth we possess,

10
00:00:28,520 --> 00:00:30,400
the more problems we need to resolve.

11
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:32,840
It's hard to define happiness.

12
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,280
To me, my happiness

13
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:37,640
is to protect my loved one.

14
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:42,280
There's a quote in "The Little Prince",

15
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,040
"One runs the risk of weeping a little

16
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:49,040
if one allows oneself to be tamed."

17
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,400
Love, however,

18
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,240
is a game for brave souls.

19
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:58,240
If being composed and rational

20
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,280
is considered sensible,

21
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:02,560
then being brave, pure,
loyal, and certain

22
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:03,840
is awakening.

23
00:01:06,320 --> 00:01:08,640
In this noisy world,

24
00:01:08,640 --> 00:01:12,440
I hope to meet a brave and pure man.

25
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,200
You're the bravest

26
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,240
and purest girl

27
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:18,840
I've met in this world.

28
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:26,120
It's similar to the line
in "The Little Prince".

29
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,400
What

30
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,720
do you mean?

31
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,640
Is it

32
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,440
not obvious enough?

33
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,960
Why do you like a rookie?

34
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,680
That's just liking.

35
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,320
There's no reason.

36
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,080
If I could give you reasons,

37
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,400
it wouldn't be considered liking.

38
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,600
In the world of love,

39
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,400
there should be
no precisions or schemes.

40
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,680
Otherwise, it turns into an evaluation

41
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,120
where people weigh the pros and cons.

42
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:08,160
How many rookies
have you evaluated before?

43
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:13,160
Speaking of love relationships,

44
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,440
to be frank with you,

45
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,520
I'm also a rookie.

46
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,560
For real?

47
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,280
Yes.

48
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:20,760
Well.

49
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,880
I'll consider it.

50
00:02:43,010 --> 00:02:46,340
[New message, Receiver, Sender]

51
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,480
Let's go home.

52
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,320
They are fast.

53
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,080
The PR department is just an excuse.

54
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,880
How are you going to deal with it?

55
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,520
Shareholders only want real profits,

56
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,600
not something with no actual value.

57
00:03:21,920 --> 00:03:23,200
The shares I have

58
00:03:23,200 --> 00:03:24,720
can bring profits to the company.

59
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,080
They won't do anything to me.

60
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,480
I know you can handle all crises

61
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,560
on your own.

62
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,800
But this time,

63
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:37,720
can you leave it to me?

64
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,720
It turns out

65
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,440
that you've been staying
in Zhen's place.

66
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,800
The scandal between you

67
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,520
has been making the rounds
in the office.

68
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,320
The stock price won't stop dropping.

69
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,800
The two of you

70
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,640
have really disgraced me.

71
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,000
Mom.

72
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,240
Nothing is going on between me and Zhen.

73
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,840
Don't believe in nonsense.

74
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:18,320
The harm is done.

75
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,320
Stop defending.

76
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,200
Mom.

77
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:25,120
I apologize for the harm

78
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,120
I brought to the company.

79
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:29,360
What is done can't be undone.

80
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,520
Later, I'll give the shareholders

81
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,480
an explanation.

82
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,520
I will bear all the responsibilities

83
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,080
for whatever happens
during the meeting later.

84
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,080
You!

85
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,040
What a disgrace.

86
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,720
To think the Anshi Group

87
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:55,360
has such fluff pieces
on the front pages.

88
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,710
[Anshi Group]

89
00:04:56,730 --> 00:04:57,960
The affair between
the brother and sister-in-law

90
00:04:58,280 --> 00:05:00,280
is outrageously unethical.

91
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,120
I'm too embarrassed to talk about it.

92
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,640
Then why are you bringing it up now?

93
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,600
This is colossal nonsense.

94
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,280
I was there.

95
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,800
It could also be
a scandal between the sisters-in-law.

96
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,640
I was with...

97
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,440
Stop it.

98
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,440
First of all,

99
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,760
I'm sorry if my personal behavior

100
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,040
has affected the company's image.

101
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,920
But, for the record,

102
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:23,040
the media misrepresented the truth.

103
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:24,760
I believe what I saw.

104
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,760
The truth is laid bare in the pictures.

105
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,000
Who else could they be except for you?

106
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,960
By right,

107
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,960
it's acceptable for two young people

108
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,120
to be in love.

109
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,160
The thing is, you're dating

110
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,400
your own brother-in-law.

111
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,520
This is inappropriate, right?

112
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,960
Mr. Wang is right.

113
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:43,400
Everyone believes in what they see.

114
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,760
But are Ms. Yan and Mr. Chu

115
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,960
really in these pictures?

116
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,520
There's no need
to examine the pictures again.

117
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:58,720
If not them,

118
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,720
is it you two?

119
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,320
Mr. Wang.

120
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,880
You really need

121
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:04,480
to put on reading glasses.

122
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,520
What did you say?

123
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,880
It does look like Ms. Yan

124
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,160
from the front.

125
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,160
However, as for the back-view pictures
where two people stand close by,

126
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,800
when zoomed in,
the body shape of the woman

127
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,000
is different from Ms. Yan's.

128
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,760
I think

129
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,200
they are just wearing similar clothes,

130
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,280
and the paparazzi edited the pictures

131
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,040
to create a fake scandal.

132
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:22,720
Rest assured, everyone.

133
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,440
The PR Department has already proceeded
with the counterplan.

134
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:27,920
I'll explain
during the press conference.

135
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:30,360
That was useless.

136
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,040
Now, Anshi Group's

137
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,600
sales performance and reputation

138
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,160
have already been affected.

139
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,960
This is the real problem

140
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,200
we need to resolve now.

141
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,200
Exactly.

142
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:41,200
The public won't care about the truth
even if you explain.

143
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,120
The point is
that the stock market has turned bad.

144
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,840
Even if you're not afraid of rumors,

145
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:47,760
it's better to lie low

146
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,120
at this rate.

147
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,200
What are you trying to get at?

148
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,480
We've discussed it

149
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,880
and we all agreed

150
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,840
that you need a break

151
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,320
to rest.

152
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,200
Yes.

153
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,160
Mr. Chu Jr. has been back for a while.

154
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,480
It's time for him to take over.

155
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,560
I support Mr. Chu Jr.

156
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,840
to be the new CEO.

157
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:13,360
Zejia's body

158
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,760
hasn't been found yet.

159
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,320
We have the right to suspect

160
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,200
that if she qualifies

161
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,800
to inherit Zejia's shares.

162
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,400
Rightfully so, Mr. Wang.

163
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,560
This time, I come back

164
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,320
to reclaim everything

165
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:34,320
that belongs to the Chu family.

166
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:35,960
It's true

167
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,680
that Yan Zhen isn't suitable

168
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,320
for the role of the group's CEO.

169
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,200
I'm more than willing

170
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,040
to take over the Anshi Group

171
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:44,480
as the new CEO.

172
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:05,840
♪Waiting for the wilted flower
to finally fall silent♪

173
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:09,640
♪Waiting for the time
to divide the sunset glow♪

174
00:08:09,850 --> 00:08:13,370
♪He stalks my mind and memories♪

175
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:17,280
♪Struggling in this perpetual cycle♪

176
00:08:17,670 --> 00:08:21,320
♪Promises are answering his lies♪

177
00:08:21,460 --> 00:08:24,970
♪I'm just a walker-on
in this tear-jerker♪

178
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:28,620
♪Tick, tock, tick, tock♪

179
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:31,840
♪Tears are speaking♪

180
00:08:32,570 --> 00:08:36,190
♪Mist blinds his eyes
from seeing rose graffiti♪

181
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:40,230
♪The dialogue sounds hoarse,
I can only hide my words within♪

182
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:44,100
♪Love me, will you? Quiet, silly♪

183
00:08:44,130 --> 00:08:47,060
♪Or just let it go?♪

184
00:08:47,060 --> 00:08:50,200
[Stars are set alight so that one day
each one of us may find our own.]

